&quot;The combination of the banking operations of Barclays <PLACE country="ES" form="NAM" gazref="IGDB:19596523" id="Pl-6" latLong="40.000°N 4.000°W" type="COUNTRY">Spain</PLACE> and
Zaragozano will bring together two complementary businesses, creating
