said in a statement.

&quot;The acquisition of Banco Zaragozano builds on our existing business
creating the sixth largest private sector banking group in <PLACE country="ES" form="NAM" gazref="IGDB:19596523" id="Pl-7" latLong="40.000°N 4.000°W" type="COUNTRY">Spain</PLACE>&quot; by
assets, added Jacobo Gonzalez-Robatto, chief executive of Barclays
<PLACE country="ES" form="NAM" gazref="IGDB:19596523" id="Pl-8" latLong="40.000°N 4.000°W" predicative="true" type="COUNTRY">Spain</PLACE>.

&quot;It provides a platform for us to intensify and strengthen our
